# Web Shell

- `web/app` is a React + TypeScript shell over the KMP web bridge exported from `kmp/core`.
- Keep browser UI, Vite setup, and bridge adaptation here.
- Prefer consuming shared state from the bridge rather than reimplementing business logic in TypeScript.
- If the required shared API is missing, update `kmp/core` bridge code instead of inventing a parallel web-only contract.
- Check `web/app/README.md` when working on bridge setup or build integration.
